  "texts": [
    "This is discussed in consideration to the current level of criminalization, which weakly implicates the parties at fault.",
    "The issues raised above relate to our discussions in Sects.",
    "3.2 and 3.3, specifically where a combination of automated 3-D capture and HPE methods could generate trivial solutions for producing deep-fake pornography.",
    "Proposals to address this include: highlighting awareness, applying due-diligence when collaborating with external partners and getting involved in research that aims at developing countermeasures (Belanger 2024; Wiggers 2024).",
    "Developing robust countermeasures that are easy to implement would provide significant advantages to researchers who wish to publish state-of-that-art models or datasets without contributing to greater social and ethical problems -such those that stemmed from publishing StableDiffusion (Downing 2024)."
  ]
}